videos.headline: Trayce Jackson-Davis throws down the hammer for Indiana
videos.description: Trayce Jackson-Davis rises up for the massive dunk in the lane.

videos.headline: Race Thompson gets way up for the huge one-handed alley-oop
videos.description: Race Thomson goes full stretch to catch and flush the one-handed alley-oop for Indiana.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Race Thompson gets way up for the huge one-handed alley-oop) 2023/03/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kebba Njie takes flight for the emphatic putback slam

videos.headline: Jalen Hood-Schifino's potential game-tying 3 catches front rim for Indiana
videos.description: Indiana's comeback attempt falls just short as Penn State holds on to book a spot in the Big Ten tournament championship game.
